      "source": [
        "**Key Findings:**\n",
        "* Data quality is good for missing values is good.\n",
        "* The data is right-skewed with most transactions under 500, but outliers reach up to ~ 1900.\n",
        "* Fort Worth, Los Angeles, and Charlotte are the top locations for account activity.\n",
        "* We identified specific IP addresses and Device IDs associated with multiple accounts (up to 13 accounts per IP), which could be an indicator of fraud rings.\n",
        "* There is a mix of high-frequency vs. low-frequency accounts, with some accounts having 10+ transactions."
