        "We created the \"delta_t\" aka time since previous transaction, and the \"balancetoAmountRatio\".\n",
        "\n",
        "* The \"delta_t\" helps us see if there are transactions occuring at a very high pace compared to the last transcation. Example: if someone was doing a lot of transactions in a short time frame unexpectedly, that could imply fraud.\n",
        "* The \"balancetoamountratio\" helps us flag any transactions that are representing a high percentage of the total account balance. This is helpful but we should take a grain of salt since people might be getting a house or large purchase and saving up."
